README.md
     1вҶ’# debug
     7вҶ’A tiny JavaScript debugging utility modelled after Node.js core's debugging
     8вҶ’technique. Works in Node.js and web browsers.
     9вҶ’
    10вҶ’## Installation
    16вҶ’## Usage
    73вҶ’#### Windows command prompt notes
    75вҶ’##### CMD
    77вҶ’On Windows the environment variable is set using the `set` command.
    78вҶ’
    79вҶ’```cmd
    80вҶ’set DEBUG=*,-not_this
    81вҶ’```
    82вҶ’
    83вҶ’Example:
    84вҶ’
    85вҶ’```cmd
    86вҶ’set DEBUG=* & node app.js
    87вҶ’```
    88вҶ’
    89вҶ’##### PowerShell (VS Code default)
    91вҶ’PowerShell uses different syntax to set environment variables.
    92вҶ’
    93вҶ’```cmd
    94вҶ’$env:DEBUG = "*,-not_this"
    95вҶ’```
    96вҶ’
    97вҶ’Example:
    98вҶ’
    99вҶ’```cmd
   100вҶ’$env:DEBUG='app';node app.js
   101вҶ’```
   102вҶ’
   103вҶ’Then, run the program to be debugged as usual.
   104вҶ’
   105вҶ’npm script example:
   106вҶ’```js
