   110вҶ’## Namespace Colors
   116вҶ’#### Node.js
   118вҶ’In Node.js, colors are enabled when stderr is a TTY. You also _should_ install
   119вҶ’the [`supports-color`](https://npmjs.org/supports-color) module alongside debug,
   120вҶ’otherwise debug will only use a small handful of basic colors.
   121вҶ’
      вҶ’вҖҰ
   124вҶ’#### Web Browser
   126вҶ’Colors are also enabled on "Web Inspectors" that understand the `%c` formatting
   127вҶ’option. These are WebKit web inspectors, Firefox ([since version
   128вҶ’31](https://hacks.mozilla.org/2014/05/editable-box-model-multiple-selection-sublime-text-keys-much-more-firefox-developer-tools-episode-31/))
   129вҶ’and the Firebug plugin for Firefox (any version).
      вҶ’вҖҰ
